abstract: British online retailer The Hut Group (THG) said it raised 1 billion euros (857.37 million pounds) to help fund expansion, amid macro-economic and political changes arising from Brexit and the general election.
snippet: British online retailer The Hut Group (THG) said it raised 1 billion euros (857.37 million pounds) to help fund expansion, amid macro-economic and political changes arising from Brexit and the general election.
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - British online retailer The Hut Group (THG) said it raised 1 billion euros (857.37 million pounds) to help fund expansion, amid macro-economic and political changes arising from Brexit and the general election.
headline_main: UK's Hut Group Raises One Billion Euros for Expansion
headline_print_headline: UK's Hut Group Raises One Billion Euros for Expansion

abstract: Asking prices for British houses fell this month by the smallest amount for any December since 2006, a survey showed on Monday, pointing to some upside for a housing market subdued by Brexit and election uncertainty.
snippet: Asking prices for British houses fell this month by the smallest amount for any December since 2006, a survey showed on Monday, pointing to some upside for a housing market subdued by Brexit and election uncertainty.
lead_paragraph: LONDON — Asking prices for British houses fell this month by the smallest amount for any December since 2006, a survey showed on Monday, pointing to some upside for a housing market subdued by Brexit and election uncertainty.
headline_main: Asking Prices for UK Houses Post Smallest December Drop Since 2006-Rightmove
headline_print_headline: Asking Prices for UK Houses Post Smallest December Drop Since 2006-Rightmove

abstract: A state-run television network pre-empted an English Premier League match between Manchester City and Arsenal after Mesut Özil denounced the mass detention of Uighurs.
snippet: A state-run television network pre-empted an English Premier League match between Manchester City and Arsenal after Mesut Özil denounced the mass detention of Uighurs.
lead_paragraph: A state-run television network in China canceled a live broadcast Sunday of an English Premier League soccer match after the Arsenal star Mesut Özil publicly condemned the country’s treatment of fellow Muslims.

abstract: The president said he wanted to target anti-Semitic speech on campuses, but in the time of new nationalism, nothing is really that simple.
snippet: The president said he wanted to target anti-Semitic speech on campuses, but in the time of new nationalism, nothing is really that simple.
lead_paragraph: President Trump’s executive order targeting anti-Semitic and anti-Israel speech on campuses might be framed as a narrow legal matter, but it has touched on a defining issue of our time: Who belongs, and who decides?

abstract: The economic losses sustained during a bruising 19-month trade war will not be easy to make up.
snippet: The economic losses sustained during a bruising 19-month trade war will not be easy to make up.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Trump administration officials predicted big gains for the economy from a newly announced trade deal with China, but the economic losses sustained during a bruising 19-month trade war will not be easy to make up.

abstract: Mario Sandoval was sent to his native country to face charges of crimes committed during the dictatorship. In France, many wonder why it took so long.
snippet: Mario Sandoval was sent to his native country to face charges of crimes committed during the dictatorship. In France, many wonder why it took so long.
lead_paragraph: A former police officer from Argentina who has lived for more than 30 years as a university lecturer and security expert in France was extradited and arrived on Monday in his native country, where he is wanted for crimes against humanity, including torture, committed during the country’s dictatorship, the French lawyer representing Argentina said.

abstract: British Prime Minister Boris Johnson will welcome 109 new Conservative lawmakers to parliament on Monday, promising to honor his election pledges to get Brexit done as soon as possible and boost funding to the state health service.
snippet: British Prime Minister Boris Johnson will welcome 109 new Conservative lawmakers to parliament on Monday, promising to honor his election pledges to get Brexit done as soon as possible and boost funding to the state health service.
lead_paragraph: LONDON — British Prime Minister Boris Johnson will welcome 109 new Conservative lawmakers to parliament on Monday, promising to honor his election pledges to get Brexit done as soon as possible and boost funding to the state health service.
headline_main: Welcoming New Lawmakers, British PM Johnson Vows a Speedy Brexit
headline_print_headline: Welcoming New Lawmakers, British PM Johnson Vows a Speedy Brexit

abstract: Letters and recordings keep a family connected, 75 years after the Battle of the Bulge.
snippet: Letters and recordings keep a family connected, 75 years after the Battle of the Bulge.
lead_paragraph: Morey Moseson didn’t know what he wanted to be when he grew up. Not for lack of options — the world seemed impossibly full. He was the class valedictorian, and the class clown. He loved to dance to Benny Goodman and Glenn Miller. His sister, Lee, two years older, taught him how to do the Lindy hop. They’d practice the eight-count step late at night, big band swing notes at 78 r.p.m. filling the rooms of their home in Jamaica, Queens.
headline_main: What Was Lost in ‘the Last Good War’
headline_print_headline: What Was Lost in ‘The Last Good War’

abstract: California is spending $187 million to try to ensure an accurate count of its population. The Texas Legislature decided not to devote any money to the job. Why?
snippet: California is spending $187 million to try to ensure an accurate count of its population. The Texas Legislature decided not to devote any money to the job. Why?
lead_paragraph: EDINBURG, Texas — Next month, California will uncork a $187 million campaign to prod its nearly 40 million residents to participate in the 2020 census. Neighborhoods across the state have been computer-ranked by how likely residents are to fill out census forms. Custom marketing campaigns are being focus-grouped. Nonprofit organizations have been showered with grants to boost response in hard-to-count areas.

abstract: Here is how a hand gesture long seen as innocuous was appropriated to signify “white power.”
snippet: Here is how a hand gesture long seen as innocuous was appropriated to signify “white power.”
lead_paragraph: Touching the thumb and index finger to make a circle, with the remaining three fingers held outstretched, is a gesture that people around the world have made for centuries, mostly in positive contexts.
